          <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4 mb-8">
            <p class="text-blue-700">This documentation provides comprehensive information on how to use SupplyFlow, the inventory management system designed specifically for small to medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) in Ghana's retail and distribution sectors.</p>
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">What is SupplyFlow?</h2>
          <p>SupplyFlow is a comprehensive inventory and supply chain management system designed specifically for small to medium-sized businesses. The platform provides real-time inventory tracking, supplier management, automated ordering, mobile accessibility, and offline capabilities to help businesses optimize their inventory management processes.</p>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-8">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-5">
