        <div class="prose prose-blue max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Getting Started with SupplyFlow</h2>
          
          <p class="mb-8">This section will guide you through the initial setup process for your SupplyFlow account and help you configure your system for optimal performance.</p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">Account Setup</h3>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-6 mb-8">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-medium mb-4">Step 1: Create Your Account</h4>
            <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-3 mb-6">
              <li>Visit <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">app.supplyflow.com/signup</a> and enter your email address.</li>
              <li>Choose a strong password for your account.</li>
              <li>Enter your business information (name, contact details, address).</li>
              <li>Select your subscription plan (Basic, Standard, or Premium).</li>
              <li>Complete the verification process by clicking the link sent to your email.</li>
            </ol>
            
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4">
              <p class="text-yellow-700 text-sm"><strong>Note:</strong> You'll need to verify your email address before you can access all features of SupplyFlow.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">Initial Configuration</h3>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-6 mb-8">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-medium mb-4">Step 2: Set Up Your Business Profile</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-6">
              <li>Navigate to Settings → Business Profile</li>
              <li>Upload your company logo (recommended size: 200x200px)</li>
              <li>Set your business hours</li>
              <li>Configure regional settings (currency, date format, etc.)</li>
              <li>Save your changes</li>
            </ul>
            
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg mb-6 overflow-hidden">
              <div class="bg-gray-50 px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200">
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600">Screenshot: Business Profile Settings</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="w-full max-w-md bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-200 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400">Logo</div>
                    <div class="ml-4">
